00:16:23,770 --> 00:16:27,400
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}It is time to listen to your heart.

146
00:16:27,560 --> 00:16:29,440
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}But the spirits around me...

147
00:16:29,610 --> 00:16:35,030
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Can help, but only the spirit within can guide you.

