{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Easy up, men!

152
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:42,850
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Here we go. Right-o. Over here.

