154
00:17:45,020 --> 00:17:45,850
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Hoist away!

155
00:17:46,020 --> 00:17:50,190
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I will honour my vow not to break the peace with the pale ones,

