{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Cut a notch in this staff for every pale face you see.

158
00:18:02,280 --> 00:18:04,240
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Watch over my daughter.

159
00:18:33,230 --> 00:18:35,360
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}I can't take you this time.

