00:18:39,110 --> 00:18:42,240
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Stay out of mischief and look after one another.

161
00:19:15,190 --> 00:19:18,820
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Do not forget this land.

