00:19:18,990 --> 00:19:21,030
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You will always be with me.

163
00:19:59,650 --> 00:20:01,150
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Wait. What's this?

