{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}Yes, of course. This was a good idea, wasn't it?

169
00:20:24,590 --> 00:20:27,050
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}This will be fine. Fantastic.

