00:23:13,100 --> 00:23:15,640
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}and I'll not have you disrupting my crew.

187
00:23:15,810 --> 00:23:17,930
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}You can take this voyage below...

