00:23:19,770 --> 00:23:22,440
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}...or in the brig.

189
00:23:22,600 --> 00:23:24,730
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}- You're...  - A guest of the king,

