{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}# Cabbages and onions #

228
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:05,030
{\fnCambria\bord1\shad1\1c&H45DFEC&\b0\i1}- Look up!  - Who's that?

